{
  "texts": [
    "Similar audits have assessed content moderation consistency across platforms [148].",
    "In a similar vein, to measure AT improvements under Articles 24 and 30, audits can evaluate completeness, formats, and accuracy of political ad disclosures before vs after DSA roll-out [163].Computational Analysis Advanced computational techniques like machine learning and network analysis allow scalable unstructured data investigations to evaluate impacts of critical DSA provisions.",
    "For instance, natural language classifiers enabled by neural models can audit samples of platform content containing warning flags or misinformation markings before and after implementation to quantify accuracy, truthfulness and contextual alignment [106].",
    "This tackles identified criticisms around transparency and proportionality of counter-measures under Article 27 [38,43,68,180].",
    "Separately, temporal analyses tracking toxicity trends or categorizing discourse by topics using sentiment modeling and dynamic topic classifiers provide vital indicators of ecosystem impacts resulting from risk mitigation efforts under Article 26 [119,145]."
  ]
}